eller metric.\nTowards the proof of our main result, we give equivalent characterizations of\nstrongly contracting elements and produce new examples of group actions with\nstrongly contracting elements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Jan 2014 18:29:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 Jan 2014 21:15:00 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 21 Feb 2015 05:57:56 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 9 Mar 2015 13:13:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-20"}
